manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Are you struggling with pain from sitting for a long time, hard seats, fatigue from driving? Our Rongbaor extra-large gel seat cushion may help you. The size is about 18.5 x 16.5 x 1.6inch, weight about 3.75lb. It can effectively alleviate hip and waist pain caused by prolonged sitting. And relieve the fatigue of sedentary.

Breathable And Cooling Cover The air mesh cover is breathable and allows for a maximum amount of air flow through the gel cushion. and the honeycomb cooling structure reduces heating between the buttocks and the seat. Even if you sitting for a long time, it can still Keep fresh and comfortable at all days. Zipper Design, Easy To Carry And Clean Our gel seat cushion has 2 newly designed cushion covers with a handle for easy carrying. and the cover has a zipper design that can be easily removed to be washed by machine. The seat cushion also can be taken out for washing. Non-slip, Fits Most Chairs The skid-resistant microdots at the back of the chair cushion keeps it in place on slippery seating surfaces. So the cushion is pretty suitable for office chairs, car chairs, wheelchairs, sofa and so on.

1. How to use: Some customers like to take off the cover and use it directly, and some customers like to use the seat cushion with the cover. There will be two different seat feelings. It depends on your preference. 2. About cleaning method: The cloth cover can be disassembled and cleaned, the seat cushion is recommended to be washed by hand. 3. About size: A. The size marked on the page is the size of the seat cushion itself, so you need to remove the cloth cover when measuring the size; B. Due to the elasticity of the gel material, there will be a little difference in the size obtained after the product is directly stretched or compressed manually, so the error value of length and width is within 1cm, and the error value of thickness is within 0.5cm. 4. About storage: Please use it on a flat surface to extend the service life, and store it in a cool environment when it is not used for a long time.It is not recommended to fold the seat cushion for a long time.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on April 7, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars It no longer hurts to sit in my office chair
reviews.reviewText: I have been in pain for about two, maybe three months. It hurts to sit on my lazy butt so it's kind of one of those things that I have ignored because I should probably walk around more anyway. But it was getting to the point that it hurt to walk because the backs of my legs, right below my rump, were hurting so badly. My desk chair at work is fine and it's not worn out. I think I just sit too much.I ordered this thinking maybe it would work. I just got it, so I have no idea if it is sturdy and will last for a while or not, but if it doesn't, then I know I just need to get a pricier version of the same thing.It is not soft like a big cushion or anything. The pad is firm-soft. So it almost feels like you are sitting on a water bed maybe? Like you are sitting on a waterbed when someone is laying on the other side so it's a little firm?I don't know if this would bring new life to a totally worn out chair, but it definitely helps with a decent but maybe under-padded chair. Worth the price.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on March 8, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars I like it. But it slides.
reviews.reviewText: I’m 6’ and about 190. This cushion does a good job in the fact that it’s very comfortable in my desk chair. No problem there.My beefs are that it’s not very grippy as it claims. It does slide around a bit when I get up, etc.. it’s livable. And my other beef is that the description is a little confusing? It states cushionS. Shows an image of cushionS. I didn’t necessarily need two cushions, but the title and description is a little misleading.So, if you’re thinking that your getting TWO CUSHIONS, you’re not. You’re getting a cushion with 2 covers. One black cover and one grey cover.Speaking of cushions, no idea about the difference between purple, black or blue cushions. Maybe I missed that (too) in the description? Bottom line - works well. But I would imagine that all of the identical looking cushions to this on Amazon are, well, identical. So pick the cheapest one.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 24, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Wouldn’t use this on my 8hr chair
reviews.reviewText: This is good for a few hours on an old chair with basically no cushion left. Couldn’t use it for 8 hours unless it was on a newer chair with some cushion life still left. The added height is good for my long legs. Maybe better overall for someone that weighs less than 200lbs. Handle makes it convenient for something to be used at stadiums or similar venue, but it would be nice if there was a snap on the handle to go around the part of an office chair that holds the back.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Size and quality
reviews.reviewText: I really love the seat cushion not only is it a good size but it is extremely comfortable and gives my back a lot of relief

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 15, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great pain helper -- a nice surprise.
reviews.reviewText: I use this as a back cushion when I am sitting in my regular chair. I also sleep on it as a pillow. It helps my injured neck & back more than I imagined.It is made of very strong sturdy materials and I think it will last for a good amount of time.It's very firm but it has a lot of give.This material is too heavy to be portable, so I use it only at home.This was a pleasant surprise & it gave me much more relief for my chronic spinal pain & fibromyalgia than I thought possible.I may get another one to sit on as my lumbar pillow is falling apart after a year or so.To all of all you good folks dealing with pain, you might give this a try.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on June 16, 2021
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars XXL Cushion for Booty
reviews.reviewText: Received my product faster than expected 👍🏽!I have been using it since day one upon arrival and let me say this cushion is awesome!It is soft but firm enough to hold my supersized backside.I do crafts and online business for hours at a time and that means being on my tush for a long extensive amount of time. I was using pillows at first but that wasn’t really working very well but this cushion so far is a relief to my buttocks.It keeps in place, it’s large enough to accommodate my BBW 🍑 and is soft and relieves the ache I use to have when just using pillows or nothing.It has a zippered cover to take off for easy cleaning and you can just take it any where you travel it’s flexible and easy to fit in any bag. I have use it so far on my chair and on car rides. I would suggest this product because it does give relief for those sitting on hard surfaces or want extra support and cushion for their bum. Excellent product so far.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 6, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Different shape from one purchased previously...not as comfortable... but better than other types!!
reviews.reviewText: (I'm updating this review to say that the Cushion is the BEST type I've ever bought. I have several health/back issues and it has really helped...I just prefer the previous shape for MY particular needs.) I purchased one a while back and decided to get another as a backup...However this "newer" one is too oblong shaped where the other had a slight curve in it...I have a spine issue and this one DOES NOT feel as good as the other shape...Very disappointed...I've spent hundreds & hundreds of dollars on different cushions that are just sitting in a closet...Previous gel pad shape was better for MY needs but this one will still be used...

reviews.reviewTitle: The best of many similar offerings.
reviews.reviewText: I recently acquired an almost exact looking fusion on Amazon which was almost 20 dollars more. Another chair needed one so I noticed these were quite a bit less expensive. (all Amazon listings) and ordered it, thinking that I would be saving a pile at the expense of a little less quality/heft BUT the opposite is the deal! Though they both had that cool patterned purple inner component, the cheaper one was a bit thicker and better suited for its application in relieving sciatic pain. (side note: relief is a loose term when talking bout sciatica. Hurts to say the word!) All in all a great deal.

It took me a month in my wheelchair to try everything to get this seat to “stay in one place” for it to work. I could not keep it from stretching and making it hard to sit without sliding forward. I am 140 lbs. Because I wanted this to work, and took so long to get it to work, I cannot return it! Now I just have a “stretchy piece of silicone” to store somewhere. Please do not include “wheelchair “ in your description.
